title: AlphaTALKS Wall Street Breakfast, June 26: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha

description: Fed speakers were out in force this week following last week's surprisingly hawkish FOMC meeting. Equity markets like what they heard, with all three major indices posting new record highs and gains of more than 2% for the week. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices
